    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本债券收益率和银行股因日本央行加息押注而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/japan-bonds-fall-on-growing-view-boj-a-step-closer-to-rate-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本政府债券收益率和银行股周三大幅上涨，因为投资者认为货币政策制定者最终有望在短期内废除负利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/japan-bonds-fall-on-growing-view-boj-a-step-closer-to-rate-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 01:13:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行称印度债券将吸引1000亿美元的外国资金流入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/hsbc-says-indian-bonds-set-for-new-era-with-100-billion-flows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰资产管理公司表示，受全球债券指数纳入的吸引，印度债券未来几年可能会吸引约 1000 亿美元的外资流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/hsbc-says-indian-bonds-set-for-new-era-with-100-billion-flows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西门子能源公司盈利大幅增长，天然气和电网势头强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/siemens-energy-earnings-beat-amid-gas-grid-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西门子能源公司(Siemens Energy AG)公布了好于预期的季度业绩，创下两个多月以来的最大涨幅，这是在这家德国制造商的风电业务遭遇一系列失败之后的积极进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/siemens-energy-earnings-beat-amid-gas-grid-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 19:18:51 GMT</pubDate>
